description: Twin Grill is providing the streets of the Twin Cities with incredibly delicious Mexican cuisine!You’ve gotta stop by this acclaimed truck because their richly flavorful selection of tortas, quesadillas, tacos, nachos, carne asada, and more, will absolutely hit the spot. And if you wish to provide your guests at your next event with the “best food in town”, have Twin Grill come cater!
name: Twin Grill
